581
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:44,840
What should we do then?

582
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:48,300
Perhaps I can set up a smaller array.

583
00:40:48,300 --> 00:40:51,670
It doesn't require any Ice Crystals, but you can only view the past.

584
00:40:51,670 --> 00:40:53,570
You can't interact with it.

585
00:40:53,570 --> 00:40:55,300
Okay.

586
00:41:08,020 --> 00:41:12,080
